{"word":"Passover","slug":"passover","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Passover</b> Institution of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=49'>Exo 12:49</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=18'>Exo 23:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=18'>Exo 34:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=8'>Lev 23:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=9&verse=5'>Num 9:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=9&verse=14'>Num 9:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=28&verse=25'>Num 28:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=16&verse=8'>Deu 16:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=16&verse=16'>Deu 16:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=81&verse=3'>Psa 81:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=81&verse=5'>Psa 81:5</a><br/> Design of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=28'>Exo 12:28</a><br/> Special Passover, for those who were unclean, or on journey, to be held in second month<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=9&verse=12'>Num 9:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=30&verse=4'>2Ch 30:4</a><br/> Lamb killed by Levites, for those who were ceremonially unclean<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=30&verse=17'>2Ch 30:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=35&verse=11'>2Ch 35:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=6&verse=20'>Ezr 6:20</a><br/> Strangers authorized to celebrate<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=49'>Exo 12:49</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=9&verse=14'>Num 9:14</a><br/> Observed:<br/> - At place designated by God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=16&verse=7'>Deu 16:7</a> <br/> - With unleavened bread<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=8'>Exo 12:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=20'>Exo 12:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=13&verse=3'>Exo 13:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=13&verse=6'>Exo 13:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=15'>Exo 23:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=6'>Lev 23:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=9&verse=11'>Num 9:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=28&verse=17'>Num 28:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=16&verse=4'>Deu 16:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=12'>Mar 14:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=7'>Luk 22:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=3'>Act 12:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=5&verse=8'>1Co 5:8</a> <br/> Penalty for neglecting to observe<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=9&verse=13'>Num 9:13</a><br/> Reinstituted by Ezekiel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=45&verse=24'>Eze 45:24</a><br/> Observation of:<br/> - Renewed by the Israelites on entering Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=5&verse=11'>Jos 5:11</a> <br/> - By Hezekiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=30&verse=1'>2Ch 30:1</a> <br/> - By Josiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=23'>2Ki 23:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=35&verse=1'>2Ch 35:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=35&verse=18'>2Ch 35:18</a> <br/> - After return from captivity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=6&verse=20'>Ezr 6:20</a> <br/> - By Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=20'>Mat 26:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=15'>Luk 22:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=2&verse=13'>Joh 2:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=2&verse=23'>Joh 2:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=13'>Joh 13</a> <br/> Jesus in the temple at time of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=50'>Luk 2:50</a><br/> Jesus crucified at time of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=2'>Mat 26:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=2'>Mar 14:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=28'>Joh 18:28</a><br/> The lamb of, a type of Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=5&verse=7'>1Co 5:7</a><br/> Lord's supper ordained at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=28'>Mat 26:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=25'>Mar 14:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=20'>Luk 22:20</a><br/> Prisoner released at, by the Romans<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=15'>Mat 27:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=6'>Mar 15:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23&verse=17'>Luk 23:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=39'>Joh 18:39</a><br/> Peter imprisoned at time of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=3'>Act 12:3</a><br/> Christ called our Passover<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=5&verse=7'>1Co 5:7</a><br/><a href='S:Feasts'>Feasts</a>"}]}